  title="Euler's Formula Is the EML Operator"
  description="eml(ix, 1) = exp(ix) = cos(x) + i·sin(x). The deepest identity in mathematics, stated as one EML node."
  date="2026-04-19"
>
  <div class="meta">
    <span>2026-04-19</span>
